We use a 4x4x4 k-qrid for the nscf and a 2x2x2 q-grid for phonon.  


Use the input files in the example01:
replace: 
* nscf.in in the nscf directory
* ph-ref.in in the phonon directory
* si.win in the wann directory 
* qe2pert.in in the qe2pert directory 

Run qe2pert to obtain your own si_epwan.h5 and then run `ephmat` using the input files example02 for perturbo


Here we provide the ephmat computed from our cluster; we also provide our own si_epwan.h5 for reference.